	
	Request For Authorization: 
If the status is “Request For Authorization” Waiting for approval we need to approve from our team.
 
	Planning In Progress:
If the status is “Planning In Progress”.  Waiting for other teams to approve.
 
	Scheduled:
If the status is “Scheduled” all  teams has been approved.
 
	Implementation In Progress:
If the status is “Implementation In Progress” then only we are able to proceed the deployment.
 
	Post Implementation Task:
Once done our implementation task, we have to mark our task in remedy as “Closed”. If the CR window time has elapsed it will indicated red color, like below screen shot.
 
Note: Make sure confirm with requester before start the deployment ask to change the CR implementation status to “Implementation In Progress”
